---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Regulatory Disclosures">
  <section class="bg-white pt-[120px] pb-24 px-6" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3mss">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:5xygiu">
      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="hidden lg:block" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:4d4fk2">
        <div class="sticky top-[120px]" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:5xygit">
          <h3 class="text-dark font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[12px] mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:oppicb">Compliance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0 m-0" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:compliance-nav">
            <li data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9abomz">
              <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-[#00A896] text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9sap9s">Privacy Policy</a>
            </li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9abomy">
              <a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-[#00A896] text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9sap9t">Terms of Service</a>
            </li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9abomx">
              <a href="/regulatory-disclosures" class="text-[#00A896] font-semibold text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:9sap9u">Regulatory Disclosures</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="max-w-[800px]" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:5xygis">
        <h1 class="text-dark text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:4n4c2z">Regulatory Disclosures</h1>

        <div class="space-y-10" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:5xygir">
          <section data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3mst">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:a1al4q">1. No Offer or Solicitation</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:2ocsk1">
              The information contained on this website does not constitute an offer to sell, a solicitation of an offer to buy, or a recommendation for any security, investment product, or service. Capital deployment is subject to definitive legal documentation and rigorous due diligence.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3msu">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:a1al4p">2. Investment Risks</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:2ocsk2">
              Alternative investments, early-stage venture capital, and private equity carry a high degree of risk. Historical performance is not indicative of future results. Investors and founders should be aware that capital may be fully at risk and illiquid for extended periods.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3msv">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:a1al4o">3. Regulatory Compliance</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:2ocsk3">
              SPVH Private Limited operates as a specialized holding company in accordance with the Companies Act, 2013, and applicable guidelines set forth by the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI) and the Reserve Bank of India (RBI). Specific investment vehicles within the SPVH ecosystem may hold separate regulatory registrations.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3msw">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:a1al4n">4. Forward-Looking Statements</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:2ocskp">
              Certain materials on this platform may contain forward-looking statements regarding market trends, business strategies, or future performance. These statements involve inherent risks and uncertainties. Actual results may differ materially from those projected.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:ur3msx">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:a1al4m">5. Advisory Disclaimer</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/regulatory-disclosures.astro:2ocskq">
              SPVH does not provide tax, legal, or accounting advice through this public platform. Users and prospective partners should consult their own professional advisors prior to entering into any transaction.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
